  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育数据同步系统画一张架构图。核心问题是GradeSync模块如何与ContentCDN、LMS Portal等组件交互。我想把BARG作为核心节点，它代表GradeSync的议价逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，BARG是GradeSync的议价核心。那ContentCDN在图里怎么命名？我看到代码里是DEF？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DEF",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，DEF就是ContentCDN。它负责定义内容分发策略，比如那个\"45%\"的阈值规则。DEF会向BARG输出定义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DEF",
        "BARG",
        "defines 45%"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把DEF到BARG的连线加上，标注\"defines 45%\"。另外SOFT也是GradeSync的一部分吧？它代表软件层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SOFT",
        "DEF",
        "BARG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，SOFT是软件实现层。它会影响BARG的议价策略，我标注为\"affects bargaining\"。还有COMP，这是LMS Portal的合规模块，会给BARG添加约束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SOFT",
        "COMP",
        "BARG",
        "affects bargaining",
        "adds constraints"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加SOFT和COMP到BARG的关系。那GOV呢？也是GradeSync的一部分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GOV",
        "SOFT",
        "COMP",
        "BARG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GOV是治理模块，它会改变VFI的边界。VFI是ContentCDN的另一个视图，代表虚拟设施接口。GOV对VFI的操作是\"shifts boundaries\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GOV",
        "VFI",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "shifts boundaries"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以VFI和DEF都是ContentCDN，只是不同视角？那DISC呢，它从LMS Portal指向VFI？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VFI",
        "DEF",
        "DISC",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，DISC是调度中心，它给VFI增加负载，标注\"adds load\"。还有ABF，这是数据反馈模块，从BARG feeding data回DEF。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DISC",
        "VFI",
        "ABF",
        "BARG",
        "DEF",
        "adds load",
        "feeds data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加ABF和DISC的关系。现在BARG有很多输出：resets rules到DEF、tightens audits到COMP、extends deals到SOFT、sets integration terms到GOV。这些都要画吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG",
        "DEF",
        "COMP",
        "SOFT",
        "GOV",
        "resets rules",
        "tightens audits",
        "extends deals",
        "sets integration terms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "全部都要，这是BARG的核心影响力。另外VFI和DISC都要连到OUT，OUT是StudentDB，最终的数据出口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VFI",
        "DISC",
