    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加了VFI到OUT的\"spillover demand\"和DISC到OUT的\"occupancy loop\"。OUT还要连到POL对吧？POL也是ContentCDN？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OUT",
        "POL",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "media pressure"
