    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "POL是政策层，也是ContentCDN的视角。OUT给POL施加\"media pressure\"，然后POL会\"changes stance\"影响BARG。还有OUT直接触发BARG的\"crisis response\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
